%% Source of truth: Spast.md §11.2
%% Owners: src/spank/inputs/hec_receiver.py, src/spank/indexing/indexer.py
%% Covers HEC ingest path with indexer ack.

sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  participant C as HEC Client
  participant R as Receiver
  participant P as RequestProcessor
  participant Q as Indexer Queue
  participant W as IndexWriter
  participant B as Bucket (SQLite)

  C->>R: POST /services/collector/event (body)
  R->>R: read headers, enforce max_content_length
  R->>P: RequestBundle(body, auth, channel)
  P->>P: auth, gzip decode, parse, validate fields
  P->>Q: put_nowait(Rows, ack_ids)
  alt queue full
    P-->>R: RequestOutcome(code=9, 503)
    R-->>C: 503 code 9
  else enqueued
    P-->>R: RequestOutcome(code=0, 200)
    R-->>C: 200 {ackId}
  end
  Q->>W: batch dequeue
  W->>B: INSERT (WAL write + fsync at checkpoint)
  W->>R: commit(ack_ids)  [monotonic watermark]
  C->>R: POST /services/collector/ack {channel, acks:[...]}
  R-->>C: {acks: {n: true/false}}
